message.body: Baby, what is going on in your life? Is everything ok? I'm worried
Yes, everything's totally fine. Ive just had a hard time talking about the Tim thing, but I'm doing well. Are you working tonight?
I quit at pranna so I'm going to be going out tomorrow but I will be free in the morning. I'm glad to hear you're doing well - it was just weird that I didn't
About it so I was concerned...
I have rehearsal tomorrow morning but I'm free later on into tomorrow night.
Ok let's shoot for that. Promise everything is ok? I thought things with timmy were going so well
It was going well for a long distance relationship which is still pretty rough. It wasn't an easy decision but it was the right one. I really am ok, just super busy with school and work now
